data.description: Beautiful 2-Story brick accent home on large corner lot with wood privacy fenced backyard. The main level features a spacious 2-story foyer, formal living & dining combo room, open eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, large family room with wood burning & gas starter fireplace. The upper level features a huge owner's suite, and private bath with dual vanities, separate tub/shower, and his/her closets. Addition upper level features include 3 additional bedrooms and a hall bathroom. Great location near Loganville and Snellville with easy access to schools and shopping.
